text: Jovana Stojanović (; born 10 February 1995) is a Serbian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Serbia women's national team. ==Career== Stojanović has been capped for the Serbia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian women's footballers Category:Serbia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:ŽFK Crvena zvezda players
